snippet.title: Freerice:  Have Fun, Get Smarter, Help End Hunger
snippet.description: For every question you answer right, our sponsors send the cash equivalent of 10 grains of rice to WFP, who use it to save and change lives around the world. Get the app on iOS and Android today, or visit beta.freerice.com to play!
